### Chat with local
POST http://localhost:5051/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Hello, local agent!" }
  ],
  "model": "mixtral-8x7b-instruct-v0.1"
}

### List directory
POST http://localhost:5051/local/dir
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "."
}

### Read file
POST http://localhost:5051/local/read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "README.md"
}

### Run command
POST http://localhost:5051/local/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cmd": "ls -la"
}